Some COVID-19 patients on Friday staged a protest at the Federal Teaching Hospital in Gombe. ‪This is coming days after a similar incident happened at the Kwadom Isolation Centre in Yamaltu Deba Local Government Area of the state. The protesting patients said they were on the streets over lack of food supply and medical attention.  



